		<title>18Racing Stables at Everleigh</title>
		<content> The racehorse training stables at     
 Everleigh form the village's largest  
 employer, employing 26 people as      
 grooms, jockeys etc.                  
 The stable provides accommodation for 
 up to 75 racehorses, from 1 to 3 year 
 old. The owners of the horses residing
 as far apart as Singapore, South      
 Africa, Hong Kong, Barbados and       
 Trinidad.                             
 The area covered by the stables       
 amounts to six to seven acres with    
 gallops rented from the Ministry of   
 Defence.                              
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
